{"tid":1108153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］ 巴黎 聖母院notre-dame cathédrale 發生大火","createTime":"2019-04-15T17:55:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T04:17:57.000Z","uid":42852,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"9c0e519b51cd33ae13bad5cc4f44ddc51dfb39e0","tid":1108153,"uid":42852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T17:55:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wz5WVNF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWz5WVNF.png&h=7ae9ab7a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4ZcRKF1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4ZcRKF1.png&h=5427291a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nA fire has broken out at the famous Notre-Dame cathedral in Paris.<br />\n<br />\nThe cause of the blaze was not immediately clear, but officials say that it could be linked to renovation work.<br />\n<br />\nImages on social media show plumes of smoke billowing into the air above the <span style=\"color: red;\">850-year-old Gothic building.<br />\n</span><br />\nLast year, the Catholic Church in France launched an urgent appeal for funds to save the cathedral, which was starting to crumble.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbedbf84ce1c237bfe569f8a3c6e73a9308b8b24","tid":1108153,"uid":42852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T17:55:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/av/world-europe-47941749/notre-dame-fire-flames-have-broken-out-at-the-cathedral-in-paris\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-europe-47941749%2Fnotre-dame-fire-flames-have-broken-out-at-the-cathedral-in-paris&d=BdEUjZUsFG%2BHnlCy9NhCdwexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=e1daa63b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.co